### Adding New Classes: Cl_EvidenceOfInsurability, Cl_InterestRate, and Cl_ReinstatementCondition (Reification) ###
:Cl_EvidenceOfInsurability a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:label "Evidence of Insurability" ;
    rdfs:comment "A document or proof submitted to verify the Insured's health or insurability status." .

:Cl_InterestRate a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:label "Interest Rate" ;
    rdfs:comment "The rate applied to overdue premiums during reinstatement, specified by the Company." .

:Cl_ReinstatementCondition a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:label "Reinstatement Condition" ;
    rdfs:comment "A reification class modeling the three required conditions for reinstating a lapsed policy: written request, evidence of insurability, and payment of overdue premiums with interest." .

### Adding New Object Properties for Reification: hasReinstatementCondition, hasEvidenceOfInsurability, hasInterestRate, hasOverduePremiums ###
:hasReinstatementCondition a owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:domain :Cl_Reinstatement ;
    rdfs:range :Cl_ReinstatementCondition ;
    rdfs:label "has Reinstatement Condition" ;
    rdfs:comment "Links a reinstatement event to its required conditions." .

:hasEvidenceOfInsurability a owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:domain :Cl_ReinstatementCondition ;
    rdfs:range :Cl_EvidenceOfInsurability ;
    rdfs:label "has Evidence of Insurability" ;
    rdfs:comment "Links a reinstatement condition to the submitted evidence." .

:hasInterestRate a owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:domain :Cl_ReinstatementCondition ;
    rdfs:range :Cl_InterestRate ;
    rdfs:label "has Interest Rate" ;
    rdfs:comment "Links a reinstatement condition to the applicable interest rate." .

:hasOverduePremiums a owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:domain :Cl_ReinstatementCondition ;
    rdfs:range :Cl_MonetaryAmount ;
    rdfs:label "has Overdue Premiums" ;
    rdfs:comment "Links a reinstatement condition to the amount of overdue premiums to be paid." .

### Instantiating Reinstatement Conditions and Linking to Reinstatement Event ###
